Package: UBL
Type: Package
Title: An Implementation of Several Approaches to Utility-based Learning for both Classification and Regression Tasks
Description: Provides a set of functions that can be used to obtain better predictive performance on cost-sensitive tasks (both regression and classification). This includes resampling approaches, cost-based methods, special purpose evaluation metrics as well as specific learning systems.
Version: 0.0.3
Depends: R(>= 3.0), methods
Imports: uba
Remotes: url::http://www.dcc.fc.up.pt/~rpribeiro/uba/uba_0.7.5.tar.gz
Suggests: MASS, rpart, testthat, DMwR
Date: 2016-03-11
